site_name: 1-9 Ratcliffe Cross Street and land to the south of 8-12 Ratcliffe Street
description: Demolition of existing workshop at 1-9 Ratcliffe Cross Street and redevelopment to provide part 7 and part 8 storey residential comprising of 56 flats ( 30 x 1 bed, 13 x 2 bed, 13 x 3 bed) with associated ground floor car park and cycle parking. Development of land to the south of 8-12 Ratcliffe Cross Street to provide an 8 storey residential comprising of 22 flats ( 8 x1 bed, 7 x 2 bed, 7 x 3 bed) with associated undercroft car and cycle parking and protected roof top child play space.
